msg: Allow jars inside the .sar to declare dependencies on Extensions. The Extensions are provided by "Optional Packages" as defined by guide/extensions/versioning.html in the jdk1.3 docs.
This allows us to have a central repository of "Optional Packages" that multiple applications could declare dependencies upon. The default extensions repository is in ${phoenix.home}/ext
